  "comments": "<p>This marks the Fourth series issued, the banknote features Ultraviolet security features on both sides:<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/64a1985c6e834.png\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/64a1985c6e834.png\" alt=\"\"></a><br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/64a19871c9c9d.png\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/64a19871c9c9d.png\" alt=\"\"></a><br>© gyoschak</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Security thread:</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Windowed into five sections on the obverse side, when seen under a backlight, the inscription of “CIMA $1” is repeated throughout.</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/671c6cbb8b26b.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/671c6cbb8b26b.jpg\"></a></p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">© Kiet Tran</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">Yellow iridescent stripe on reverse side - inscription “$1”:</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\"><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/671c6db966ca0.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/671c6db966ca0.jpg\"></a></p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">© Kiet Tran</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin-left:0px;\">For the 2024 issue, the title of Managing Director was updated to Chief Executive Officer.</p>",
